desc: We want every bar, in ever wrapper, to taste as good as a hand-baked cake, while only being made with real, wholefood ingredients. We will never use chemicals, binders, flavours, preservatives, or anything artificial, and we will make every single bar by hand.

layout.text: 100% Organic and plant-based packaging, tested to decompose in your home compost bin in 26 weeks, leaving no toxic residues - just nutrient dense soil.
